Content:
COPPER BEYOND
Possibly the best luxury buffet in Bangkok. Copper beyond not only serve more than 200 all you can eat items, even oysters, sashimi, wagyu beef and lobster are all unlimited.

Just download and make your reservation through Hungry Hub app to secure your slots to enjoy the deal at 2599baht ($103sgd).

📍Gaysorn Amarin, Unit 3F-s06, 3F-s07 502, Phloen Chit Rd, Lumphini, Pathum Wan, Bangkok 10330, Thailand

