Ideal for gathering or dating! 🍻 

@o.bba_sg has been our go-to spot whenever we crave Korean food! The food quality is consistently on point and authentic to taste, especially their charcoal-grilled Prime Beef Short Rib, Seafood Jjajangmyeon and Tteokbokki!

Tried booking through @hungryhub_sg for the first time and the experience was pretty decent! You can find many worthy deals (up to 50% off) that are exclusively available on this online platform! We foresee ourselves using it again for our next food outing.. 🤭 &

